You can verify that PostGIS 2.5.4 is installed and enabled as an extension in the
            database with this
            query.SELECT * FROM pg_available_extensions WHERE name = 'postgis' ;

After running the script, you can verify that PostGIS 2.5.4 is installed and enabled
            as an extension in a database with this
            query.SELECT * FROM pg_available_extensions WHERE name = 'postgis' ;
